{"tid":548880,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一風堂 可一不可再","createTime":"2018-02-03T05:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T07:10:49.000Z","uid":156183,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d40a2df832622818d8ba4a67e9ed1dbf7f06d4","tid":548880,"uid":156183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"今日去中環蘭桂芳附近間一風堂食野，第一次去，叫左兩個拉麵，一個豚肉飯， 唔夠五分鐘佢拎左碟類似炒芽茶既物體黎，以為前菜，食左三分一大約過左五分鐘，個waiter行過黎話碟炒雜菜你地無叫架喎，跟著收左碟炒雜菜，轉頭俾埋張單我地，計埋我地錢。 火都黎，跟著同佢講你擺低我點知你係咪前菜，未食完收左我地重要計錢，佢話你地食左。 跟著我話咁你拎過碟新既黎俾我地食返。  吊，明明飽到死重要食多碟炒芽菜，on9<br />\n<br />\n呢間升級版味千真係可一不可再<br />\n<br />\n唔通我叫細拉麵，佢俾大拉麵我，食左又要收返大拉麵價。垃圾服務重要收加一，都仲要成條龍排隊，香港人奴性極重"},{"pid":"6d9b9a81d0e07603425b616c16233ed621b4dec3","tid":548880,"uid":156183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/133240_6e53c04f8204d07e5f27e090c62892d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F133240_6e53c04f8204d07e5f27e090c62892d7.png&h=78b0f6f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f41457b16290954b38a7aa80989b9e6ecd2dc576","tid":548880,"uid":156183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/133347_df10c8d57c15baeb6a5e76311ae3d8d8.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F133347_df10c8d57c15baeb6a5e76311ae3d8d8.png&d=zRDvmxCS8mYNeMIDAQYKsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=89a22958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/03/133347_df10c8d57c15baeb6a5e76311ae3d8d8.png</a>"},{"pid":"e913e253a1b98a7a00a6bd9dd9edb1e4db62490b","tid":548880,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:11:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a890ca1861ba42a45b14dc2b5809a6d620cf144","tid":548880,"uid":1167,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"